1
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,159
You came because of

2
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:37,519
those rumors, right?

3
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:39,799
About us two,

4
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,200
I bet everyone in your household

5
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,040
knows it by now.

6
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:45,799
Probably.

7
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,359
As for who started it,

8
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:52,239
it's easy to guess.

9
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,680
Can't be more than three people.

10
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:56,359
For a young lady,

11
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:57,840
this kind of thing's awkward to handle.

12
00:01:58,319 --> 00:01:58,959
So…

13
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:00,799
maybe I should step in.

14
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,959
What are you planning to do?

15
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,079
Simple.

16
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:08,719
I'll come propose.

17
00:02:20,439 --> 00:02:21,080
No,

18
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:23,879
that's way too fast!

19
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:26,000
Aren't we still figuring things out?

20
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:29,159
Please don't do anything yet.

21
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,639
I can handle it myself.

22
00:02:31,639 --> 00:02:33,000
Since everyone already knows,

23
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,919
we might as well

24
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:35,439
make it official.

25
00:02:36,159 --> 00:02:36,680
No.

26
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,919
I still need time to think.

27
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,599
Please, I'm begging you.

28
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:50,960
Alright.

29
00:02:51,439 --> 00:02:53,120
We'll do it your way.

30
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,879
You should head to the palace.

31
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,599
State matters are waiting for you.

32
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,639
I'm off then.

33
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,400
I'll wait for your message.

34
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:28,120
Nannies, what are you…

35
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,680
What are you doing?

36
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:33,080
You little brat,

37
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,400
always running your mouth!

38
00:03:34,439 --> 00:03:35,199
Gonna send you somewhere
that'll teach you a lesson!

39
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:36,639
Hold it.
Move!

40
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,800
What's all this?

41
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,439
Miss Qingpu, save me!

42
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:41,159
Behave yourself!

43
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,599
What a coincidence.

44
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,120
I wanted to tie her up too.

45
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,159
How about

46
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,240
you hand her over to me?

47
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:49,280
Mother!

48
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:51,919
Mother.

49
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,439
I heard everything.

50
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,039
Sorry for troubling you.

51
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,439
Lian!

52
00:03:58,439 --> 00:03:59,680
Mother.

53
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:01,520
Why would you do this?

54
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:04,400
Mother, I was just mad at her.

55
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,280
Why should she

56
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:07,360
steal my savings

57
00:04:07,719 --> 00:04:08,360
and still expect me

58
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,240
to cover up her scandal?

59
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,400
Why should I?

60
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,560
Her scandal?

61
00:04:13,599 --> 00:04:15,080
That's Chen Yanyun!

62
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:17,319
But didn't you tell me

63
00:04:18,319 --> 00:04:19,160
that Chen Yanyun

64
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,000
just keeps her as a mistress?

65
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,120
Mistress or not,

66
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,360
she's still

67
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,680
his woman!

68
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,279
If Chen Yanyun hears

69
00:04:26,519 --> 00:04:28,199
you've been spreading rumors

70
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,040
about her and another man,

71
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:32,120
he'll never let it slide.

72
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,680
So what?

73
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,959
Chen Yanyun may be powerful,

74
00:04:39,079 --> 00:04:39,959
but can he really meddle

75
00:04:39,959 --> 00:04:41,279
in our family business?

76
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:44,519
I'm gonna get back at Gu Jinzhao!

77
00:04:45,519 --> 00:04:47,240
So what if she has Chen Yanyun?

78
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,240
I still have Wenxiu,

79
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,600
and the Yao family!

80
00:04:51,079 --> 00:04:51,959
I'm not scared of her!

81
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:53,560
Compared to Chen Yanyun,

82
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,120
the Yao family means nothing!

83
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,800
If you keep causing trouble outside,

84
00:04:58,079 --> 00:04:59,399
you'll get your father killed someday

85
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:01,040
and bring disaster to our whole Gu family!

86
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,839
Please calm down, Mother.

87
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,079
Mother,

88
00:05:06,759 --> 00:05:07,759
Lian was really

89
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,399
reckless this time.

90
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:12,079
But it's not that serious, is it?

91
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:13,800
At worst,

92
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:15,800
we apologize in private

93
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:16,839
and let it go.

94
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:18,720
If this really gets exposed,

95
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:19,959
even Chen Yanyun

96
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:21,959
would lose face.

97
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,279
What do you know?

98
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:27,079
Deyuan's career

99
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,120
will be ruined by you sooner or later!

100
00:05:46,199 --> 00:05:47,600
Ma'am!

101
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:48,480
It's bad!

102
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,000
Tang wasn't sent away and

103
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,439
Ms. Jinzhao got her.

104
00:05:53,519 --> 00:05:54,600
Ms. Jinzhao is here!

105
00:05:58,639 --> 00:06:00,160
Grandmother, Auntie.

106
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,680
Lian is here too.

107
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,199
Seems everyone's here,

108
00:06:04,199 --> 00:06:05,720
saved me the trouble of going around.

109
00:06:09,399 --> 00:06:10,959
No need for that tone.

110
00:06:11,959 --> 00:06:13,279
I know you've been wronged.

111
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:14,680
I've heard

112
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,759
about the rumors too.

113
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,720
Your Auntie has been
investigating all day.

114
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,519
We've figured it out now.

115
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,079
It was Tang who spread them.

116
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,519
I was just about to send someone

117
00:06:25,959 --> 00:06:26,720
to arrest her.

118
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,399
We were thinking the same thing.

119
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:32,680
Grandmother, you're truly wise.

120
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,439
But I think

121
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,759
Tang wouldn't have done it

122
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:36,600
for no reason.

123
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,439
Someone must have ordered her.

124
00:06:40,879 --> 00:06:42,240
Right, Tang?

125
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,319
Tang,

126
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,759
don't you dare talk nonsense.

127
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,600
Tang,

128
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,279
if Qingpu hadn't arrived in time,

129
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:57,879
you'd already

130
00:06:58,199 --> 00:06:59,920
be sent to the estate.

131
00:07:07,079 --> 00:07:08,360
It was Ms. Lian who told me to do it.

132
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,360
She told me to go to Baoxiang Temple!

133
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,160
Ms. Lian sent you there

134
00:07:12,399 --> 00:07:13,800
to pray for a

135
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,079
consecrated bracelet,

136
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:17,000
not to spread nonsense here

137
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,959
and ruin her reputation!

138
00:07:19,959 --> 00:07:20,879
Exactly!

139
00:07:21,079 --> 00:07:22,680
I never told you to spread rumors!

140
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:23,839
Miss,

141
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,560
it was you who sent me!

142
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,600
If you hadn't taught me,

143
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,000
how could I have ever said those things?

144
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:29,439
You…

145
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:33,000
Don't you dare twist the truth!

146
00:07:33,399 --> 00:07:34,040
Mother.

147
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:35,120
Nanny Su.
Yes!

148
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:36,319
Slap her!
Yes!

149
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:44,199
Ms. Jinzhao,

150
00:07:44,639 --> 00:07:45,439
it really was Ms. Lian who told me
to spread rumors

151
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:47,399
about you and Mr. Wang!

152
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:48,560
And,

153
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:50,279
she specifically sent me
to Baoxiang Temple,

154
00:07:50,439 --> 00:07:51,959
saying I should spread it
among the servants

155
00:07:52,079 --> 00:07:53,519
since many noble ladies go there to pray!

156
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,120
It was

157
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,279
all Ms. Lian's order!

158
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:57,160
I didn't!

159
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,720
I didn't!

160
00:07:58,959 --> 00:07:59,519
Grandmother.
Enough!

161
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:01,959
Tang

162
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:03,199
was originally

163
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:04,920
Lian's personal maid.

164
00:08:05,439 --> 00:08:07,040
Since you spread rumors on your own

165
00:08:07,319 --> 00:08:08,279
and falsely accused your miss…

166
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,720
Have her flogged 20 times,

167
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,560
then send her to the estate,

168
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:14,240
never allow her to return to the capital!

169
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:16,319
Grandmother,

170
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:18,639
Tang deserves punishment,

171
00:08:18,879 --> 00:08:20,240
no matter what it is.

172
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,480
But don't forget,

173
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,720
the one behind this is Lian.

174
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:24,879
Don't show favoritism.

175
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,399
Why are you so anxious?

176
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,920
Who said I'm protecting Lian?

177
00:08:31,639 --> 00:08:32,519
Lian

178
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:33,799
failed to discipline her servants

179
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,320
and let a mistress suffer.

180
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:36,440
She must be punished too.

181
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,240
20 slaps to the palm,

182
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:40,840
and three days kneeling

183
00:08:41,159 --> 00:08:42,039
in the ancestral hall.

184
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,360
Grandmother…

185
00:08:44,639 --> 00:08:45,399
What?

186
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,080
That's too light!

187
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:48,919
Gu Jinzhao, listen up,

188
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:49,960
don't push your luck!

189
00:08:50,559 --> 00:08:52,000
Lian knows she was wrong.

190
00:08:52,519 --> 00:08:53,360
Thank you, Mother.
We accept the punishment.

191
00:08:54,279 --> 00:08:55,000
Let's go.
We'll take our punishment!

192
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,600
We know we were wrong!

193
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,519
Nanny Su.

194
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,519
Drag that wench out now!

195
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,639
Got it. Someone here!

196
00:09:01,879 --> 00:09:02,840
Drag her out!

197
00:09:03,039 --> 00:09:03,759
Ma'am!

198
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:05,440
Ma'am, I'm innocent!

199
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:05,919
Move!

200
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:07,679
My lady made me do it all!

201
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,159
- I'm innocent!
- Move!

202
00:09:09,639 --> 00:09:10,720
Ma'am!

203
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,559
All of you out.

204
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:13,679
Jinzhao, you stay.

205
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:14,519
Yes.

206
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:16,519
Qingpu, you go too.

207
00:09:17,399 --> 00:09:17,919
Yes.

208
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:22,720
Grandmother,

209
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,960
what are you trying to do?

210
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:31,000
Jinzhao,

211
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,399
don't look at me like that.

212
00:09:35,679 --> 00:09:36,600
About this matter,

213
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,000
I of course know

214
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:40,279
it's Lian's fault.

215
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:46,519
But your auntie

216
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:48,279
has only one

217
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:50,240
legitimate daughter.

218
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,440
We can't just throw her out!

219
00:09:54,519 --> 00:09:55,879
To put it bluntly,

220
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:59,200
your reputation's already ruined.

221
00:09:59,399 --> 00:10:00,759
But if Lian's name

222
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,799
gets ruined too…

223
00:10:02,559 --> 00:10:03,679
Then our Gu family,

224
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,120
Hui, Lan,

225
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:08,080
Jinrong, Jinxian,

226
00:10:08,279 --> 00:10:09,039
what will they do?

227
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:10,799
How will they ever marry?

228
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,200
How will they live?

229
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:16,000
So the top priority now

230
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:20,159
is not punishment,

231
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,960
but how to fix this!

232
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:26,159
Looks like you already
have a plan, Grandmother.

233
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,440
Don't think

234
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,080
what you did

235
00:10:30,519 --> 00:10:32,440
that night, sneaking off to Cuizhu Residence,

236
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,279
went unnoticed.

237
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:36,159
You don't really think

238
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:38,240
you can marry Chen Yanyun, do you?

239
00:10:41,879 --> 00:10:43,679
You're overthinking it.

240
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:46,960
If Chen Yanyun

241
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:49,039
truly wanted to marry you,

242
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:50,600
why would he

243
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,960
meet you in secret,

244
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,519
instead of openly

245
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:54,759
coming to propose?

246
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:56,960
Clearly,

247
00:10:57,159 --> 00:10:57,879
he only treated you

248
00:10:57,879 --> 00:10:59,320
like some woman outside.

249
00:11:01,759 --> 00:11:02,360
I know.

250
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,000
You don't care
about your reputation.

251
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:06,679
But the daughters of the Gu family

252
00:11:07,639 --> 00:11:09,120
cannot become someone's kept woman!

253
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,960
So the only way now

254
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,519
is for you to marry Wang Zan

255
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,840
and keep everything peaceful.

256
00:11:29,159 --> 00:11:31,000
Lian spread rumors about me and Wang Zan.

257
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,720
So Grandmother, your solution is

258
00:11:32,879 --> 00:11:33,879
to marry me off?

259
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:36,879
Looks like

260
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,799
you really value Wang Zan.

261
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:45,279
Marriage has always,

262
00:11:45,519 --> 00:11:46,240
since ancient times,

263
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,519
been arranged by one's parents.

264
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:50,159
I'm not here to discuss it with you.

265
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,200
Neither am I discussing it with you.

266
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:54,639
I will not marry him.

267
00:11:55,159 --> 00:11:56,440
You should give up on this idea.

268
00:11:56,639 --> 00:11:57,440
How outrageous!

269
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:58,879
Who allowed you

270
00:11:58,879 --> 00:12:00,320
to speak to your elders like that?

271
00:12:13,799 --> 00:12:15,240
I heard everything

272
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,600
you said to Uncle Deyuan.

273
00:12:17,039 --> 00:12:18,039
Aren't you afraid

274
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,360
that by forcing me like this,

275
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,679
after I marry into the Wang family,

276
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:21,879
I'll reveal everything

277
00:12:21,879 --> 00:12:22,960
I shouldn't?

278
00:12:25,039 --> 00:12:26,720
That is the Minister
of Justice's household!

279
00:12:27,039 --> 00:12:28,159
Do you think

280
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,360
that right now in the Gu family,

281
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:32,639
no one can do anything to you?

282
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:33,879
Someone here!

283
00:12:34,759 --> 00:12:35,440
Yes!

284
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,600
Lock her in the woodshed,

285
00:12:37,879 --> 00:12:38,600
without my order,
she's not allowed out!

286
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:39,960
Yes!

287
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,679
Who would dare!

288
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,200
Ma'am.

289
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:35,039
Mr. Ji has arrived.

290
00:13:35,559 --> 00:13:37,320
And he brought more
than ten carts of gifts,

291
00:13:37,559 --> 00:13:38,919
saying he's here to propose.

292
00:13:39,639 --> 00:13:40,279
He wants

293
00:13:40,679 --> 00:13:42,080
to marry Ms. Jinzhao.

294
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,399
Isn't that just a marriage proposal?

295
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:46,960
What's the big deal?

296
00:13:47,679 --> 00:13:49,000
So if someone comes to propose,

297
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,840
I can't punish my granddaughter?

298
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,320
Do it.

299
00:13:53,919 --> 00:13:54,759
Ma'am,

300
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,159
the Ji family serves the Chen family.

301
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:03,639
Alright.

302
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,799
Have Mr. Ji wait in the front hall.

303
00:14:07,879 --> 00:14:08,639
I'll go now.

304
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:09,639
Yes.

305
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:14,360
Have Deyuan and Dezhao returned?

306
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:16,360
Only Master Dezhao is off duty,

307
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,279
he just got back.

308
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,159
Have him go too.
Yes.

309
00:14:21,759 --> 00:14:22,879
Go quickly!

310
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:31,879
You called

311
00:14:32,039 --> 00:14:32,960
Mr. Ji here, right?

312
00:14:33,559 --> 00:14:34,279
No.

313
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,919
Then was it Chen Yanyun?

314
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,399
Of course not!

315
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:44,600
Miss.

316
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,799
Mr. Ji actually came to propose to you.

317
00:14:48,399 --> 00:14:49,519
I don't know what's going on.

318
00:14:49,759 --> 00:14:50,080
Let's go

319
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:51,200
around back and take a look.

320
00:14:52,559 --> 00:14:53,960
My greetings, Madam,

321
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:55,799
Second Madam, Fourth Master.

322
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,200
Mr. Ji,

323
00:15:02,559 --> 00:15:04,159
you want to marry Jinzhao?

324
00:15:04,639 --> 00:15:05,200
Yes.

325
00:15:06,919 --> 00:15:07,879
My Grandmother

326
00:15:07,879 --> 00:15:09,120
personally prepared the betrothal gifts.

327
00:15:09,399 --> 00:15:10,279
Madam,
and Fourth Master, please review.

328
00:15:26,799 --> 00:15:27,799
2000 taels of gold.

329
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,039
And 50,000 taels of silver?

330
00:15:33,159 --> 00:15:34,679
Mother!

331
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,080
Well,

332
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:45,799
we can talk.

333
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:49,000
I've also prepared some small gifts

334
00:15:49,559 --> 00:15:50,639
for all the elders.

335
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:51,759
Please accept them.

336
00:15:58,679 --> 00:15:59,240
Madam,

337
00:16:00,159 --> 00:16:01,759
I got this jade bracelet

338
00:16:01,759 --> 00:16:03,200
on a grain transport voyage to Toungoo.

339
00:16:03,519 --> 00:16:04,360
Wear it on your wrist,

340
00:16:04,799 --> 00:16:05,799
and it stays warm in winter
and cool in summer.

341
00:16:14,799 --> 00:16:15,559
Mr. Ji,

342
00:16:16,559 --> 00:16:17,720
you've spent too much.

343
00:16:19,039 --> 00:16:19,879
Coming from so far

344
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,200
must have been hard.

345
00:16:21,919 --> 00:16:22,600
On my word.

346
00:16:24,519 --> 00:16:25,080
Ma'am.

347
00:16:25,519 --> 00:16:27,440
Attend to Mr. Ji as he washes up,

348
00:16:27,679 --> 00:16:28,360
and,

349
00:16:28,559 --> 00:16:29,919
then escort him
to the main hall for dinner.

350
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:31,840
Yes.

351
00:16:33,559 --> 00:16:34,360
Thank you, Madam.

352
00:16:35,759 --> 00:16:36,399
Mr. Ji,

353
00:16:36,879 --> 00:16:37,440
please.

354
00:16:48,159 --> 00:16:48,720
What?

355
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,840
You dare to come propose,

356
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:51,879
but doesn't dare see me?

357
00:16:54,159 --> 00:16:55,240
Not like you,

358
00:16:55,559 --> 00:16:56,679
no shame at all,

359
00:16:56,879 --> 00:16:58,000
and you don't even protect yourself.

360
00:16:58,960 --> 00:17:00,320
You've caused such a scene,

361
00:17:00,879 --> 00:17:01,679
making Grandmother

362
00:17:01,679 --> 00:17:02,840
lose sleep for days.

363
00:17:03,919 --> 00:17:04,640
What?

364
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:07,119
Did maternal grandmother send you?

365
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:08,039
No.

366
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:09,799
Grandmother didn't mention it.

367
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,519
I came on my own.

368
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,359
I heard those
filthy rumors.

369
00:17:17,680 --> 00:17:18,720
Those are all rumors.

370
00:17:19,079 --> 00:17:20,559
I know they're rumors.

371
00:17:21,079 --> 00:17:22,279
But gossip is a deadly weapon.

372
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:24,359
Even a man can't handle it,

373
00:17:24,799 --> 00:17:26,200
let alone a young lady like you.

374
00:17:26,839 --> 00:17:28,240
I just can't stand them

375
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:29,480
spreading nonsense and ruining your name.

376
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:31,720
But you didn't have to propose!

377
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:34,240
Proposing is the best solution.

378
00:17:35,319 --> 00:17:36,039
I looked into it.

379
00:17:36,559 --> 00:17:37,319
That Wang Zan

380
00:17:37,599 --> 00:17:38,839
is a known scoundrel.

381
00:17:39,319 --> 00:17:40,200
Who knows

382
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:41,559
what trouble he'll cause in the future?

383
00:17:42,279 --> 00:17:43,920
Instead of guarding against rumors,

384
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:44,720
I'd like

385
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:46,319
to propose to you now.

386
00:17:46,920 --> 00:17:48,480
If anyone dares trouble you later,

387
00:17:48,880 --> 00:17:50,000
I'll have every right

388
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:50,799
to deal with them!

389
00:17:52,039 --> 00:17:52,680
Miss Gu,

390
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,839
Mr. Ji arrived in the capital
yesterday at noon.

391
00:17:56,079 --> 00:17:57,240
He was supposed to meet guests.

392
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:58,960
But then he heard

393
00:17:59,079 --> 00:18:00,200
you were being bullied.

394
00:18:00,359 --> 00:18:01,279
He was terribly anxious,

395
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:02,440
canceled all his appointments

396
00:18:02,599 --> 00:18:03,920
and immediately went back
to Tongzhou to prepare.

397
00:18:04,519 --> 00:18:05,400
Mrs. Ji told him

398
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,920
to wait a few days
because of the bad weather.

399
00:18:07,319 --> 00:18:08,160
But he couldn't wait

400
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:10,240
and came over today anyway.

401
00:18:10,759 --> 00:18:11,960
Just worried you'd be wronged.

402
00:18:12,319 --> 00:18:14,079
He didn't even get a sip of water,

403
00:18:14,680 --> 00:18:16,279
and broke out in mouth sores from anxiety.

404
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:17,400
Enough,

405
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:18,799
you talk too much.

406
00:18:20,079 --> 00:18:21,079
Come to my courtyard.

407
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:22,960
I'll make you lotus seed soup.

408
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:24,039
How can that be?

409
00:18:24,519 --> 00:18:25,880
I've already proposed,

410
00:18:26,599 --> 00:18:28,079
meeting like this is improper enough.

411
00:18:28,079 --> 00:18:29,519
How could I go to your courtyard?

412
00:18:31,799 --> 00:18:33,200
You, go back now,

413
00:18:33,599 --> 00:18:34,519
don't worry
about anything,

414
00:18:35,759 --> 00:18:37,160
just leave it all to me.

415
00:18:39,559 --> 00:18:40,519
You all go back.

416
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:42,400
Yes.

417
00:18:46,279 --> 00:18:47,720
How can you be so willful?

418
00:18:48,079 --> 00:18:48,559
This…
Yao,

419
00:18:51,160 --> 00:18:52,160
I'm really touched

420
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:53,799
by what you did.

421
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:56,599
But do you

422
00:18:56,799 --> 00:18:58,000
truly like me?

423
00:19:02,359 --> 00:19:03,039
I…

424
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:06,559
Of course… I like you.

425
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:08,279
Is it

426
00:19:08,279 --> 00:19:09,759
a brother's love for his sister

427
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:11,559
or is it a gentleman's

428
00:19:11,839 --> 00:19:13,160
admiration for a fair lady?

429
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:21,319
If I were to marry someone,

430
00:19:21,680 --> 00:19:22,920
it would be someone

431
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:23,960
who truly loves me

432
00:19:24,279 --> 00:19:25,400
and whom I truly love.

433
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:26,960
And also,

434
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,759
a little liking isn't enough.

435
00:19:29,079 --> 00:19:30,039
It has to be the kind

436
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:31,200
that when I think of it,

437
00:19:31,559 --> 00:19:33,200
I can't sleep night after night.

438
00:19:34,079 --> 00:19:35,680
I'd keep turning it over in my mind.

439
00:19:36,839 --> 00:19:38,000
And my face

440
00:19:38,519 --> 00:19:39,480
would even flush.

441
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:40,680
That kind of love.

442
00:19:51,839 --> 00:19:52,599
Yao,

443
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:55,400
we grew up together.

444
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:56,799
I also hope

445
00:19:56,960 --> 00:19:57,920
you can find someone

446
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,079
you truly love.

447
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:00,519
You get married,

448
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:02,079
and she becomes my sister-in-law.

449
00:20:07,519 --> 00:20:08,680
It's getting late,

450
00:20:09,200 --> 00:20:10,519
go back and rest early.

451
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:12,599
I'll have the lotus seed soup

452
00:20:12,759 --> 00:20:14,000
sent to you once it's ready.

453
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:16,720
I'll be going now.

454
00:20:27,039 --> 00:20:28,640
Can't sleep night after night.

455
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:31,240
Turning it over in her mind.

456
00:20:32,359 --> 00:20:34,400
And her face would even flush?

457
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,799
How is she so clear about it?

458
00:20:55,440 --> 00:20:56,039
Sir,

459
00:20:56,599 --> 00:20:57,880
something's wrong at Daxin Warehouse.

460
00:20:58,240 --> 00:20:58,759
Please take a look.

461
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:10,720
Bran?

462
00:21:13,319 --> 00:21:14,519
They really went that far!

463
00:21:15,799 --> 00:21:16,799
Go there yourself.

464
00:21:17,519 --> 00:21:18,039
No,

465
00:21:19,599 --> 00:21:20,759
bring the warehouse manager here,

466
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:21,960
I'll handle this myself.

467
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:23,400
Yes.

468
00:21:31,119 --> 00:21:32,519
It used to store rice,

469
00:21:32,599 --> 00:21:34,279
but half a month ago
it was switched to bran.

470
00:21:34,759 --> 00:21:35,720
The morning before last they said

471
00:21:36,039 --> 00:21:37,519
it was to be sent to Pingyang
Prefecture for disaster relief.

472
00:21:38,039 --> 00:21:39,920
I also felt something was off.

473
00:21:41,119 --> 00:21:42,400
There was clearly rice in the warehouse,

474
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:44,079
why use bran for relief?

475
00:21:44,279 --> 00:21:45,440
But I saw their

476
00:21:45,519 --> 00:21:46,720
transport documents were all complete,

477
00:21:47,039 --> 00:21:47,960
so I didn't pursue it.

478
00:21:48,319 --> 00:21:49,519
Who's in charge

479
00:21:49,559 --> 00:21:50,680
of this warehouse?

480
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:51,519
My lord,

481
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:53,119
it is Lord Sun Shitao.

482
00:21:53,599 --> 00:21:54,680
Sun Shitao?

483
00:21:55,519 --> 00:21:56,119
Sir,

484
00:21:56,799 --> 00:21:57,920
this Sun Shitao

485
00:21:57,920 --> 00:21:59,599
hasn't shown up for several days.

486
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:01,640
Then where did you get orders

487
00:22:01,640 --> 00:22:02,960
for the grain in and out
over the past two days?

488
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:06,359
My lord, look.

489
00:22:50,799 --> 00:22:51,799
Greetings, sir.

490
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:53,440
Sit.

491
00:22:54,839 --> 00:22:56,200
What happened?

492
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:58,279
Why did you have Mr. Jiang

493
00:22:58,519 --> 00:23:00,119
secretly bring me here?

494
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:01,079
Don't worry.

495
00:23:02,039 --> 00:23:03,039
Sit down, let's talk slowly.

496
00:23:07,839 --> 00:23:09,960
No one in the household noticed, right?

497
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:12,519
I've got Qingpu watching it.

498
00:23:12,839 --> 00:23:14,000
No one will find out.

499
00:23:19,079 --> 00:23:19,599
Come,

500
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:22,160
have some tea,

501
00:23:22,519 --> 00:23:23,240
it'll calm you down.

502
00:23:24,279 --> 00:23:25,799
Did something serious happen?

503
00:23:26,279 --> 00:23:27,039
Otherwise

504
00:23:27,319 --> 00:23:28,559
you wouldn't have called me here.

505
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:30,359
No matter how urgent it is,

506
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:31,680
we shouldn't jump straight into business
the moment we meet.

507
00:23:33,240 --> 00:23:34,119
How is that

508
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:36,240
any different from being
at Grand Secretariat?

509
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:40,680
I heard

510
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,240
Ji Yao proposed to you.

511
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:43,759
I didn't accept.

512
00:23:51,279 --> 00:23:51,839
By the way,

513
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:57,400
I liked it after

514
00:23:58,519 --> 00:23:59,440
trying it last time,

515
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:01,119
so I found some

516
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:02,839
for you to try.

517
00:24:11,839 --> 00:24:12,359
How is it?
Does it taste the same?

518
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:15,400
It's good.

519
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:19,720
Alright, now to business.

520
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,079
Pingyang Prefecture is in drought.

521
00:24:22,359 --> 00:24:24,240
The Ministry of Revenue
released 200,000 kg of relief grain

522
00:24:24,839 --> 00:24:26,519
from Daxin Warehouse in Tongzhou.

523
00:24:27,079 --> 00:24:28,599
But someone interfered

524
00:24:29,079 --> 00:24:30,839
and replaced the rice with bran.

525
00:24:34,599 --> 00:24:35,759
The Ministry of Revenue
is under my charge.

526
00:24:36,119 --> 00:24:36,960
And this

527
00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:38,519
happened right under my nose.

528
00:24:39,039 --> 00:24:39,920
Clearly,

529
00:24:40,519 --> 00:24:42,519
they want me to take the blame,

530
00:24:42,799 --> 00:24:43,960
but they're also afraid I won't comply.

531
00:24:44,599 --> 00:24:45,839
I'm being watched.

532
00:24:46,319 --> 00:24:47,119
That's why

533
00:24:47,559 --> 00:24:48,920
I had to trouble you

534
00:24:49,319 --> 00:24:50,279
to meet like this.

535
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:53,880
My father

536
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:55,880
is the Grain Storage Director
of the Ministry of Revenue.

537
00:24:56,759 --> 00:24:58,000
He oversees Daxin Warehouse.

538
00:24:58,720 --> 00:24:59,440
Could it be…
him?

539
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:02,039
He was kept in the dark too.

540
00:25:03,119 --> 00:25:04,680
Someone forged his official seal.

541
00:25:05,680 --> 00:25:06,200
Who?

542
00:25:06,839 --> 00:25:07,960
Your father's colleague,

543
00:25:08,559 --> 00:25:09,400
Sun Shitao.

544
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:11,400
This man was placed

545
00:25:11,400 --> 00:25:12,680
in the Ministry of Revenue
by Wang Xuanfan.

546
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,200
He's now gone missing.

547
00:25:14,519 --> 00:25:16,240
But I've already sent people to find him.

548
00:25:17,799 --> 00:25:18,839
Wang Xuanfan?

549
00:25:20,079 --> 00:25:21,160
Why would he do this?

550
00:25:21,559 --> 00:25:22,720
To bring down Fan Chuan.

551
00:25:23,759 --> 00:25:25,279
Zhao Jichang, the Shanxi
Provincial Governor,

552
00:25:25,440 --> 00:25:26,680
is Fan Chuan's brother-in-law.

553
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:27,920
This man

554
00:25:28,279 --> 00:25:29,279
is extremely greedy

555
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:30,960
and colludes with grain merchants.

556
00:25:32,039 --> 00:25:33,519
But because of Fan Chuan,

557
00:25:34,119 --> 00:25:34,960
no one dares touch him.

558
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:36,079
But,

559
00:25:36,359 --> 00:25:37,599
this disaster relief case is major,

560
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:39,319
so he has to cooperate
with the investigation.

561
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,279
And Zhao Jichang's sister,

562
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:42,839
also Fan Chuan's wife,

563
00:25:43,279 --> 00:25:44,599
is usually very ostentatious.

564
00:25:44,799 --> 00:25:46,000
She has left behind many handles.

565
00:25:46,559 --> 00:25:48,000
Once Zhao Jichang falls,

566
00:25:48,799 --> 00:25:49,680
Mrs. Fan

567
00:25:50,279 --> 00:25:51,440
won't escape either.

568
00:25:52,119 --> 00:25:52,839
By then,

569
00:25:53,119 --> 00:25:54,680
no matter how Fan Chuan
tries to clear his name,

570
00:25:56,279 --> 00:25:58,079
it'll all come crashing down
piece by piece.

571
00:25:58,440 --> 00:25:59,160
In the end,

572
00:26:00,240 --> 00:26:01,960
he'll have no choice but
to resign as Grand Secretary

573
00:26:03,519 --> 00:26:04,519
and end up in a miserable state.

574
00:26:05,519 --> 00:26:06,240
Since

575
00:26:06,799 --> 00:26:08,319
it was Wang Xuanfan's move,

576
00:26:09,519 --> 00:26:11,039
then the mastermind behind it

577
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:12,440
must be Fu…

578
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:14,519
Not certain.

579
00:26:15,119 --> 00:26:16,079
He might know,

580
00:26:16,640 --> 00:26:17,440
or he might just

581
00:26:18,039 --> 00:26:19,039
be pretending not to.

582
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:21,240
No wonder.

583
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:23,880
You knew you were being watched

584
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:25,519
but couldn't make a move

585
00:26:25,720 --> 00:26:26,799
and had to lay low here.

586
00:26:28,160 --> 00:26:29,640
Passing off bran as relief grain,

587
00:26:29,839 --> 00:26:30,599
that is

588
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:31,880
a beheading offense, right?

589
00:26:32,200 --> 00:26:33,640
And if it sparks a riot,

590
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:34,799
then…

591
00:26:35,319 --> 00:26:37,000
wiping out the whole
clan wouldn't be excessive.

592
00:26:39,400 --> 00:26:40,839
Then… the relief grain…

593
00:26:40,839 --> 00:26:41,920
It was shipped out yesterday.

594
00:26:42,559 --> 00:26:43,680
Can we still stop it?

595
00:26:48,079 --> 00:26:48,720
Probably

596
00:26:49,599 --> 00:26:50,599
not.

597
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,680
They've set up such a huge trap.

598
00:26:54,119 --> 00:26:55,599
They won't make a move

599
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:56,960
until the case blows wide open.

600
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,359
What do we do now?

601
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:01,240
Don't worry too much.

602
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:02,960
I've got a plan.

603
00:27:03,759 --> 00:27:05,880
It takes about seven days

604
00:27:06,759 --> 00:27:07,880
from the capital to Pingyang Prefecture.

605
00:27:08,279 --> 00:27:09,519
But news

606
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:11,200
from Shanxi to the capital

607
00:27:11,599 --> 00:27:12,759
by express courier

608
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:14,279
takes four days

609
00:27:14,279 --> 00:27:15,240
at most.

610
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:17,039
The grain left yesterday,

611
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:18,319
which means

612
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:20,400
we still have nine days.

613
00:27:21,359 --> 00:27:22,519
If I'm right,

614
00:27:23,119 --> 00:27:24,160
Sun Shitao

615
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,400
is probably doomed by now.

616
00:27:25,759 --> 00:27:26,960
Dead or alive,

617
00:27:27,880 --> 00:27:28,839
as long as we find him,

618
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:30,279
they won't be able to bury this so easily.

619
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:31,400
Then,

620
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:32,799
you'll have grounds to seek justice

621
00:27:32,799 --> 00:27:33,759
in Shuntian Prefecture.

622
00:27:34,599 --> 00:27:35,559
So next,
your job is

623
00:27:36,759 --> 00:27:38,079
to do whatever it takes

624
00:27:38,759 --> 00:27:39,839
to stall this case.

625
00:27:40,559 --> 00:27:41,640
The longer you drag it out,

626
00:27:42,319 --> 00:27:44,359
the more room we'll have to maneuver.

627
00:27:46,039 --> 00:27:46,880
Got it.

628
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:48,640
But,

629
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:50,359
you're Lord Chief Councilor's man.

630
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:52,279
Telling me all this,

631
00:27:52,599 --> 00:27:54,759
won't that put you in danger?

632
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:56,599
In this scheme,

633
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,279
I'm just the pawn.

634
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:00,720
Once the case breaks,

635
00:28:00,920 --> 00:28:02,720
prison will be the least of it.

636
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:04,920
So doing this

637
00:28:04,920 --> 00:28:06,160
isn't just saving yourself,

638
00:28:06,359 --> 00:28:07,400
it's saving me too.

639
00:28:09,559 --> 00:28:10,359
When the time comes,

640
00:28:10,559 --> 00:28:11,559
if I'm locked up,

641
00:28:13,119 --> 00:28:14,519
I'll be counting on you.

642
00:28:24,119 --> 00:28:25,640
Before I left Pingyang Prefecture,

643
00:28:25,799 --> 00:28:26,440
there was only one day

644
00:28:26,559 --> 00:28:27,880
of light rain.

645
00:28:28,359 --> 00:28:29,680
Barely a drop in the bucket.

646
00:28:29,920 --> 00:28:30,519
I heard

647
00:28:30,599 --> 00:28:32,400
the Provincial Bureau already
asked the capital for aid.

648
00:28:32,759 --> 00:28:33,200
The relief grain

649
00:28:33,319 --> 00:28:34,559
should arrive soon.

650
00:28:35,160 --> 00:28:35,839
I suppose

651
00:28:36,519 --> 00:28:37,519
it's nothing serious.

652
00:28:39,920 --> 00:28:41,480
The refugees must be fed,

653
00:28:42,079 --> 00:28:43,160
that's what matters most.

654
00:28:43,839 --> 00:28:45,519
If Pingyang Prefecture falls into chaos,

655
00:28:45,960 --> 00:28:46,759
then you and I,

656
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:49,519
whether we beat the drum for justice

657
00:28:49,759 --> 00:28:51,039
or cry bloody murder,

658
00:28:52,839 --> 00:28:54,920
none of it will help, we're doomed.

659
00:28:57,279 --> 00:28:58,640
How much grain

660
00:28:59,039 --> 00:29:00,079
do we have stored in Pingyang Prefecture?

661
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:02,359
After you told me to buy grain,

662
00:29:02,599 --> 00:29:04,279
I bought two batches right away.

663
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:05,839
About 3,500 kg total.

664
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,960
Then when the drought got worse,

665
00:29:08,319 --> 00:29:09,279
I spent more silver

666
00:29:09,519 --> 00:29:11,240
and gathered another thousand or so.

667
00:29:11,519 --> 00:29:12,400
Altogether,

668
00:29:12,640 --> 00:29:14,039
we have around 5,000 kg.

669
00:29:17,880 --> 00:29:18,680
5,000 kg…

670
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:21,640
That's still not enough.

671
00:29:22,440 --> 00:29:24,160
Go to Shaanxi and Henan,

672
00:29:25,039 --> 00:29:25,799
and Jiangnan too.

673
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:28,519
Even if it costs more,

674
00:29:29,079 --> 00:29:29,799
buy it all back,

675
00:29:30,119 --> 00:29:31,079
as much as you can.

676
00:29:32,519 --> 00:29:33,960
If the relief grain goes wrong,

677
00:29:34,119 --> 00:29:35,079
we'll step in

678
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:36,240
and help the government feed them.

679
00:29:39,359 --> 00:29:40,839
Get the soup kitchens

680
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:42,039
and medicine ready too.

681
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:44,319
Miss,

682
00:29:44,599 --> 00:29:45,440
what's wrong?

683
00:29:45,839 --> 00:29:46,839
How did you know

684
00:29:47,039 --> 00:29:48,720
something would go wrong
with the relief grain?

685
00:29:48,839 --> 00:29:49,640
Don't ask.

686
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:51,319
All you need to know is

687
00:29:51,519 --> 00:29:52,680
this is a matter of life and death.

688
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:54,039
We must not let the famine victims

689
00:29:54,039 --> 00:29:55,119
in Pingyang Prefecture

690
00:29:55,119 --> 00:29:55,880
rise up in revolt.

691
00:29:57,519 --> 00:29:57,960
So,

692
00:29:58,839 --> 00:30:00,720
take 50,000 taels of silver

693
00:30:01,039 --> 00:30:02,200
and make another trip to Shanxi.

694
00:30:03,519 --> 00:30:03,960
Yes.

695
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:16,319
Chen Yanyun, answer me,

696
00:30:16,640 --> 00:30:17,920
where did the grain go?

697
00:30:18,119 --> 00:30:19,000
Where did it go?

698
00:30:19,799 --> 00:30:20,480
Lord Fan!
Lord Fan.

699
00:30:21,559 --> 00:30:22,319
Lord Fan,

700
00:30:22,640 --> 00:30:23,880
there's no need for this.

701
00:30:24,599 --> 00:30:26,079
Lord Chief Councilor is not here today.

702
00:30:26,279 --> 00:30:27,079
Please calm down.

703
00:30:27,079 --> 00:30:28,319
Alright?

704
00:30:28,799 --> 00:30:30,920
Lord Fan, that's not quite fair.

705
00:30:31,319 --> 00:30:32,279
For something this big,

706
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:34,160
of course Yanyun wouldn't know.

707
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:36,680
He's in charge of the Ministry of Revenue.

708
00:30:37,079 --> 00:30:38,000
If he knew,
what would that make him?

709
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:41,359
He can't exactly admit he ordered

710
00:30:41,359 --> 00:30:42,240
the relief grain

711
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,480
replaced with bran, can he?

712
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:45,960
Whether he ordered it or not

713
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:47,000
will be clear with a single investigation.

714
00:30:49,559 --> 00:30:50,319
Chen Yanyun,

715
00:30:51,039 --> 00:30:53,000
you can't escape responsibility for this.

716
00:30:53,559 --> 00:30:55,160
If it leads to a riot,

717
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:57,240
you won't be able to atone even in death!

718
00:30:58,799 --> 00:31:00,400
Lord Fan, you're right.

719
00:31:01,119 --> 00:31:02,440
This is a major case.

720
00:31:03,119 --> 00:31:04,720
It must go through a joint trial
by the Three Judicial Departments.

721
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:05,920
At that time,

722
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:08,000
I will also have to be questioned.

723
00:31:13,359 --> 00:31:14,759
This is my resignation letter.

724
00:31:15,079 --> 00:31:15,799
Please,
Lord He,

725
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:19,279
pass it to Lord Chief Councilor for me.

726
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:20,920
Yanyun, you…

727
00:31:25,079 --> 00:31:25,720
Alright.

728
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:27,440
You…

729
00:31:28,839 --> 00:31:30,759
So you were prepared all along.

730
00:31:30,759 --> 00:31:32,720
And you still claim you knew nothing?

731
00:31:34,119 --> 00:31:36,119
This is a memorial I just drafted.

732
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:37,920
Lord He,

733
00:31:38,240 --> 00:31:39,640
please pass it to
Lord Chief Councilor as well.

734
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:44,400
You…

735
00:31:44,720 --> 00:31:46,160
You're trying to impeach Lord Fan?

736
00:31:47,559 --> 00:31:48,240
What?

737
00:31:49,359 --> 00:31:51,440
Impeach me for what?

738
00:31:52,119 --> 00:31:53,839
I impeach you

739
00:31:54,559 --> 00:31:55,799
for promoting your wife's brother,

740
00:31:56,079 --> 00:31:58,119
Zhao Jichang, the Shanxi
Provincial Governor

741
00:31:58,400 --> 00:31:59,799
and for shielding his illegal acts

742
00:32:00,079 --> 00:32:01,279
with your position.

743
00:32:01,839 --> 00:32:03,000
A total of ten charges.

744
00:32:05,839 --> 00:32:07,599
Very well, Chen Yanyun.

745
00:32:08,079 --> 00:32:09,400
So this is your scheme,

746
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:10,000
isn't it?

747
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:12,160
You set Zhao Jichang up first,

748
00:32:12,440 --> 00:32:13,720
then impeach me.

749
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:16,799
So I'd be forced to resign in disgrace

750
00:32:16,799 --> 00:32:18,039
and step out of the Grand Secretariat!

751
00:32:18,039 --> 00:32:18,960
Right?

752
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:22,119
Did Fu Hailian know about this?

753
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:24,759
He knew, didn't he?

754
00:32:25,240 --> 00:32:27,519
That's why he deliberately
called in sick today.

755
00:32:27,519 --> 00:32:28,440
Right?

756
00:32:31,799 --> 00:32:32,519
I'll

757
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:33,960
take my leave.

758
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:36,319
You…

759
00:33:11,279 --> 00:33:12,799
Lord Zhang, out on assignment?

760
00:33:13,079 --> 00:33:14,519
There's a severe drought
in Pingyang Prefecture.

761
00:33:14,519 --> 00:33:16,440
But the court's 200,000 kg of relief grain

762
00:33:16,440 --> 00:33:18,039
has somehow turned into bran.

763
00:33:19,920 --> 00:33:20,720
Chiliarch Ye,

764
00:33:21,319 --> 00:33:22,319
I remember your elder sister
married into

765
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:24,559
the Gu family of Daxin, right?

766
00:33:25,119 --> 00:33:25,880
Why don't you,

767
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:27,680
since you're familiar with them,

768
00:33:28,359 --> 00:33:29,640
make the trip yourself?

769
00:33:33,799 --> 00:33:34,519
Fine.

770
00:33:38,039 --> 00:33:38,599
Not just

771
00:33:38,599 --> 00:33:40,599
Gu Dezhao, the Grain Storage Director
of the Ministry of Revenue,

772
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:42,839
every male member

773
00:33:42,839 --> 00:33:43,599
of the Gu Manor,

774
00:33:43,599 --> 00:33:44,880
bring them all back.

775
00:33:45,720 --> 00:33:47,440
You're abusing your
power for personal revenge.

776
00:33:49,519 --> 00:33:51,160
This is on Lord Chief Councilor's orders.

777
00:33:51,519 --> 00:33:52,559
Don't believe it? Go ask him.

778
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:34,719
Jinzhao!

779
00:34:35,960 --> 00:34:36,679
Jinzhao!

780
00:34:39,119 --> 00:34:40,320
Ye Xian brought the Criminal
Investigation Bureau guards

781
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:40,880
to arrest people.
They're even coming for Jinrong!

782
00:34:42,239 --> 00:34:42,760
Go,

783
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:43,800
go check the front courtyard!

784
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:04,960
I really don't know what's going on!

785
00:35:04,960 --> 00:35:07,039
I've been wronged!

786
00:35:07,519 --> 00:35:08,159
Young Lord,

787
00:35:08,719 --> 00:35:10,400
please speak to higher-ups for me!

788
00:35:10,920 --> 00:35:14,159
What does this have
to do with our Censorate?

789
00:35:14,159 --> 00:35:15,159
Why am I being charged

790
00:35:15,159 --> 00:35:16,559
along with everyone else?

791
00:35:16,920 --> 00:35:18,000
And why are even

792
00:35:18,159 --> 00:35:20,440
all the Gu men implicated?

793
00:35:21,599 --> 00:35:22,199
Take them away.

794
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:23,360
Move!
Young Lord!

795
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,639
- Young Lord!
- Young Lord!

796
00:35:25,719 --> 00:35:26,119
Move!

797
00:35:26,119 --> 00:35:27,159
You can't do this!

798
00:35:27,239 --> 00:35:28,519
- This is unjust!
- Young Lord!

799
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:30,320
- Uncle!
- Young Lord!

800
00:35:30,679 --> 00:35:32,320
Uncle, why are you arresting me?

801
00:35:32,599 --> 00:35:33,119
- What on earth
- Jinzhao!
is going on?

802
00:35:34,199 --> 00:35:34,960
Jinzhao!

803
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,599
Save me, Jinzhao!

804
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:37,480
Jinzhao!

805
00:35:44,719 --> 00:35:46,239
The decree says detain for trial,

806
00:35:46,519 --> 00:35:48,199
meaning the case
hasn't been fully investigated.

807
00:35:48,639 --> 00:35:50,159
You're totally innocent.

808
00:35:50,440 --> 00:35:51,039
Once you're in prison,

809
00:35:51,119 --> 00:35:52,400
eat and sleep as usual.

810
00:35:52,679 --> 00:35:54,000
Don't take anything to heart.

811
00:35:54,519 --> 00:35:55,360
Take care of yourselves.

812
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:58,519
Come closer.

813
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:13,519
Make way.

814
00:36:17,119 --> 00:36:18,000
What's going on?

815
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:19,320
This time even Jinxian and Jinrong
are arrested.

816
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:25,239
The decree only ordered
the arrest of your father.

817
00:36:25,679 --> 00:36:27,199
That bastard Zhang Ling is taking revenge.

818
00:36:29,519 --> 00:36:30,280
Got it.

819
00:36:32,039 --> 00:36:33,360
I've already arranged things
in the prison.

820
00:36:34,079 --> 00:36:34,679
Don't worry.

821
00:36:35,880 --> 00:36:36,840
Take care

822
00:36:37,360 --> 00:36:38,159
of yourself too.

823
00:36:41,719 --> 00:36:42,679
Have they all been brought in?

824
00:36:43,360 --> 00:36:44,559
My lord, they've all been brought.

825
00:36:45,360 --> 00:36:45,960
Jinxian!

826
00:36:46,599 --> 00:36:47,280
Mother!

827
00:36:47,679 --> 00:36:48,280
Mother!
Jinxian!

828
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:49,599
Mother, save me!
Let's go.

829
00:36:50,400 --> 00:36:50,760
Yes.

830
00:36:52,440 --> 00:36:52,880
Mother!
Jinxian!
Mother!

831
00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:55,400
Ye Xian!

832
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:55,960
Mother!
Release Jinxian!

833
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:58,199
He's your own nephew!

834
00:36:59,599 --> 00:37:00,119
Ye Xian!

835
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:01,559
Ye Xian!

836
00:37:02,119 --> 00:37:02,800
- Auntie.
- Ye…

837
00:37:05,119 --> 00:37:06,599
Lord Xian is just following orders.

838
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:08,199
Too many eyes are watching.

839
00:37:08,679 --> 00:37:09,599
Don't worry,

840
00:37:09,599 --> 00:37:10,719
as long as Lord Ye is here,

841
00:37:10,840 --> 00:37:12,159
Jinxian won't suffer.

842
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:14,039
You're right.

843
00:37:16,320 --> 00:37:16,960
Jinzhao.

844
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,519
I was wrong

845
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:20,960
to pressure you before.

846
00:37:21,239 --> 00:37:22,840
You can speak to Lord Chen,

847
00:37:23,079 --> 00:37:24,039
please beg him

848
00:37:24,239 --> 00:37:25,239
to save us.

849
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:26,519
Grandmother,

850
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:28,559
it's not that I won't beg Mr. Chen.

851
00:37:29,199 --> 00:37:30,360
It's just this time,

852
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:32,360
even he may not be able to intervene.

853
00:37:33,199 --> 00:37:34,360
There's a problem
with the disaster relief grain.

854
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:35,360
He's in charge of the Ministry of Revenue,

855
00:37:35,519 --> 00:37:36,960
he'll be questioned by the
Three Judicial Departments himself.

856
00:37:38,000 --> 00:37:39,159
He might even end up in jail.

857
00:37:41,400 --> 00:37:42,519
- What do we do?
- Mother.

858
00:37:43,119 --> 00:37:44,280
What do we do?

859
00:37:44,679 --> 00:37:45,840
All the men of our household

860
00:37:45,960 --> 00:37:46,880
have been taken away.

861
00:37:47,239 --> 00:37:48,039
What do we do?

862
00:37:48,559 --> 00:37:49,840
What do we do?

863
00:37:51,039 --> 00:37:52,000
What do we do?

864
00:37:52,840 --> 00:37:53,480
Grandmother,

865
00:37:54,159 --> 00:37:55,440
it's not completely hopeless.

866
00:37:58,320 --> 00:37:59,280
The master's private seal,

867
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:00,400
all his correspondence,

868
00:38:00,760 --> 00:38:01,360
and the account books,

869
00:38:01,519 --> 00:38:02,519
bring them all out.

870
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:03,599
Don't miss a single one,
be careful.

871
00:38:04,440 --> 00:38:04,960
Got it.

872
00:38:08,039 --> 00:38:09,239
Miss, take a look at this.

873
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:17,519
Lord Chen,

874
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:19,239
I'm asking you,

875
00:38:19,960 --> 00:38:22,559
do you know why the
200,000 kg of relief grain

876
00:38:23,039 --> 00:38:24,880
ended up as bran?

877
00:38:25,920 --> 00:38:27,360
I don't know.

878
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:30,199
All grain storage and release

879
00:38:30,519 --> 00:38:32,559
must go through multiple
approvals in the Ministry of Revenue.

880
00:38:33,320 --> 00:38:34,760
As Vice Minister of Revenue,

881
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,079
in charge of the Ministry,

882
00:38:36,519 --> 00:38:37,559
how could you not know?

883
00:38:38,599 --> 00:38:40,119
It was my negligence,

884
00:38:40,679 --> 00:38:41,920
I didn't know the grain was switched.

885
00:38:42,639 --> 00:38:43,880
Your negligence?

886
00:38:48,519 --> 00:38:49,519
Both of these documents

887
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:51,280
were approved by you

888
00:38:51,599 --> 00:38:53,440
half a month ago.

889
00:38:54,400 --> 00:38:56,559
This grain-replacement document

890
00:38:57,079 --> 00:38:58,960
claims that the old grain is piling up

891
00:38:59,159 --> 00:39:00,440
and may spoil,

892
00:39:00,719 --> 00:39:02,599
which would be unfavorable
for public needs and state funds,

893
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:04,119
so it requests replacing it
with fresh grain.

894
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:07,559
Whereas the replacement order
and the allocation order

895
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:09,360
are only three days apart.

896
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:10,519
On this,

897
00:39:11,159 --> 00:39:12,519
what's your explanation?

898
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:25,360
Jinzhao,
this letter

899
00:39:26,199 --> 00:39:27,360
mentions Sun Shitao.

900
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,440
In the 35th year of Jingning,

901
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:29,320
he sought a promotion

902
00:39:29,519 --> 00:39:30,519
but was stopped by Father.

903
00:39:30,559 --> 00:39:31,239
So he poured tea

904
00:39:31,239 --> 00:39:32,599
onto the memorial Father had written.

905
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:40,159
Looks like old grudges.

906
00:39:40,639 --> 00:39:41,280
This is useful,
keep it.

907
00:39:42,880 --> 00:39:43,320
Okay.

908
00:39:44,159 --> 00:39:44,880
Lord Chen,

909
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:46,679
tell me, in the Ministry of Revenue,

910
00:39:47,199 --> 00:39:49,719
who has such ability

911
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:52,760
to manage so many people and matters

912
00:39:53,199 --> 00:39:55,679
without being discovered?

913
00:40:07,119 --> 00:40:07,840
Lord Chen,

914
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:09,519
why so silent?

915
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:11,719
I…

916
00:40:13,800 --> 00:40:14,760
have nothing to say.

917
00:40:15,599 --> 00:40:16,360
Lord Chen,

918
00:40:17,039 --> 00:40:19,000
you're a high-ranking court official,

919
00:40:19,440 --> 00:40:22,199
but this case is too serious,

920
00:40:22,519 --> 00:40:24,159
and you still say nothing.

921
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:25,639
Then I

922
00:40:25,920 --> 00:40:26,840
can only ask you

923
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:28,199
to go to the prison at the
Criminal Investigation Bureau

924
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:29,960
and stay there for a few days.

925
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:40,239
Lord Yao,

926
00:40:41,000 --> 00:40:43,440
just follow the rules.

927
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:19,840
Well?

928
00:41:20,039 --> 00:41:20,960
Did you find out?

929
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:22,440
How is Mr. Chen?

930
00:41:23,440 --> 00:41:24,920
He's been thrown into the prison at the
Criminal Investigation Bureau.

931
00:41:25,719 --> 00:41:27,280
They say he admitted negligence.

932
00:41:27,719 --> 00:41:28,559
The joint trial

933
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:29,960
ended in one hour.

934
00:41:33,199 --> 00:41:35,599
[In this game, I'm just a pawn.]

935
00:41:36,039 --> 00:41:37,239
[Once the case breaks,]

936
00:41:37,719 --> 00:41:39,440
[prison will be the least of it.]

937
00:41:40,519 --> 00:41:41,000
Jinzhao.

938
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:43,519
Jinzhao?

939
00:41:44,440 --> 00:41:45,320
I'm fine.

940
00:41:47,239 --> 00:41:48,079
He took

941
00:41:48,320 --> 00:41:49,400
everything on himself.

942
00:41:50,159 --> 00:41:50,719
Yes.

943
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:52,039
Also,

944
00:41:53,079 --> 00:41:54,360
I found a lead on Sun Shitao.

945
00:41:55,880 --> 00:41:57,039
I didn't expect

946
00:41:57,239 --> 00:41:57,679
Yanyun

947
00:41:57,679 --> 00:41:59,199
didn't even defend himself.

948
00:41:59,800 --> 00:42:01,079
He just said it was his negligence

949
00:42:01,079 --> 00:42:02,880
and took all the blame.

950
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:06,360
He didn't defend,

951
00:42:06,760 --> 00:42:08,039
not because he didn't want to,

952
00:42:08,519 --> 00:42:09,360
but because

953
00:42:09,960 --> 00:42:11,760
he saw through your plan

954
00:42:12,639 --> 00:42:14,039
and didn't call it out.

955
00:42:14,760 --> 00:42:16,320
He knew the plan

956
00:42:16,400 --> 00:42:18,079
was with your tacit approval, right?

957
00:42:21,400 --> 00:42:21,920
Yes.

958
00:42:22,639 --> 00:42:23,880
Yanyun is smart.

959
00:42:24,360 --> 00:42:26,000
But I also left clues on purpose.

960
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:27,960
So he'd cooperate, right?

961
00:42:30,519 --> 00:42:32,119
You think I didn't know?

962
00:42:32,119 --> 00:42:33,079
You deliberately

963
00:42:33,679 --> 00:42:35,000
didn't tell him.

964
00:42:36,119 --> 00:42:36,920
My lord,

965
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:38,840
I had no choice.

966
00:42:39,119 --> 00:42:40,239
Such a big deal,

967
00:42:40,239 --> 00:42:41,960
the fewer people who knew
at the start, the better.

968
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:44,159
Besides,

969
00:42:44,760 --> 00:42:45,840
Yanyun

970
00:42:45,840 --> 00:42:47,159
seems gentle on the surface,

971
00:42:47,159 --> 00:42:48,519
but he's actually quite proud.

972
00:42:50,079 --> 00:42:51,440
I was worried he wouldn't agree

973
00:42:51,679 --> 00:42:52,719
and might ruin things.

974
00:42:53,199 --> 00:42:54,119
Enough.

975
00:42:54,119 --> 00:42:55,440
Don't talk about this anymore.

976
00:42:55,440 --> 00:42:57,159
When he gets out of prison,

977
00:42:57,360 --> 00:42:58,840
I'll smooth things over

978
00:42:58,840 --> 00:43:00,000
between you two.

979
00:43:02,039 --> 00:43:03,199
How is Fan Chuan?

980
00:43:04,360 --> 00:43:05,039
He's ill.

981
00:43:05,639 --> 00:43:07,119
He collapsed as soon as
he got home that day.

982
00:43:07,880 --> 00:43:08,920
Last night he heard Zhao Jichang

983
00:43:08,920 --> 00:43:10,599
was found guilty of corruption and fraud

984
00:43:10,800 --> 00:43:12,360
and other crimes like selling state grain

985
00:43:12,599 --> 00:43:14,360
and was ordered arrested
and sent back to the capital.

986
00:43:14,719 --> 00:43:16,159
He collapsed right away.

987
00:43:17,000 --> 00:43:17,760
I'm thinking

988
00:43:18,079 --> 00:43:19,480
we can have Han Song, Wang Chuyi

989
00:43:19,480 --> 00:43:20,320
those censors

990
00:43:20,519 --> 00:43:21,400
start an impeachment.

991
00:43:22,039 --> 00:43:22,760
While he's down,

992
00:43:24,400 --> 00:43:25,079
finish him off.

993
00:43:29,840 --> 00:43:30,440
My lord,

994
00:43:30,840 --> 00:43:31,719
the Prefect of Shuntian

995
00:43:31,920 --> 00:43:33,199
just sent word

996
00:43:33,760 --> 00:43:34,280
saying

997
00:43:34,400 --> 00:43:35,679
the daughter of the Director
of the Ministry of Revenue

998
00:43:35,920 --> 00:43:37,159
filed a petition

999
00:43:37,280 --> 00:43:38,079
to the Shuntian Prefecture.

1000
00:43:38,800 --> 00:43:39,880
She said Director Gu

1001
00:43:40,920 --> 00:43:42,519
was framed

1002
00:43:43,039 --> 00:43:44,880
and she wanted justice for her father.

1003
00:43:45,559 --> 00:43:46,960
Which Director Gu?

1004
00:43:47,519 --> 00:43:48,519
The Grain Storage Director
of the Ministry of Revenue,

1005
00:43:48,880 --> 00:43:49,599
Gu Dezhao.

1006
00:43:50,360 --> 00:43:51,880
The one who signed off
on grain distribution.

1007
00:43:52,239 --> 00:43:53,880
His daughter…

1008
00:43:56,239 --> 00:43:57,159
The one

1009
00:43:58,559 --> 00:44:00,159
who competed with Yanyun

1010
00:44:00,159 --> 00:44:02,960
in archery and riding
at the spring outing?

1011
00:44:03,360 --> 00:44:04,000
Yes, that should be her.
